modName: City Forests and Landscape V2 trees
summary: City Forest is a new mod for Citys and outside citys to have Trees and foilage. more immersion into the city and game play.
descriptionHtml:
THIS IS A COMPLETELY NEW VERSION WITH DEFAULT QUEST FIXES FOR THE WHITERUN TREE.
 
Current mod supports Winterhelm, Whiterun, Riften, Solitude, Markarth.

 City Forests and Foilage for Citys. 

--TO DO-- 
Finish the rest of the towns, and fine tune foilage. these will be soon, 

--Updates--
  This will be updated weekly. sometimes daily depending on my work. 
--Thanks to--
 4ltair - Suggestion of reinstalling Whiterun Questline Tree
 Hikaru Maski - Suggestion of LOD
 
Thank you for chosing my modd, and Vote.
